Lost Girl S01E04: Faetal Attraction

Bo tries to handle being rejected by Dyson with the help of Kenzi. Dyson tries the same with Hale's help as well. A Harpy and her husband meet Bo and the Harpy tries to hire Bo to kill a human. She refuses and all hell breaks loose.

The resolution is 624x352 and the quality is good in my opinion. This episode aired on Showcase Canada on Oct 3, 2010.
